 <span data-ttu-id="88d1b-148">В разделе <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> пример, который использует это свойство.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="88d1b-148">See <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for an example that uses this property.</span></span>
